        <item>
            <title>【評測】RG RX-78-2 元祖高達 2.0     資深模型師評語：感覺似 PGU 縮細版</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/rgrx782-0/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=rgrx782-0</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/rgrx782-0/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 12:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257151</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日模型界的熱門話題，一定是 Bandai 的 RG RX-78-2 元祖高達 2.0 推出了，當年 Bandai 推出 RG 系列的首個作品，也就是 RG RX-78-2 元祖高達，當時也是非常哄動！玩具模型都是早買早享受，小編收到送測版時已是今日的事了，但上星期已有很多模型發燒友或高手早已入手，亦已見到有很多完成作品在各高達或模型羣組分享，故此小編也邀請了一位資深模型師 N.Maker 熊沛文先生，品評一下這部 RG RX-78-2 元祖高達 2.0。</p><h2>超簡單開箱</h2><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0736-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0736-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0736.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">今日收到送測的大熱 RG 2.0 元祖高達了。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0737-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0737-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0737.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">今次的膠貼紙比較少花紋，但有字的貼紙就比較多。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0738-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0738-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0738.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">素組派應該會比較喜愛的隱藏式水口。</p><h2>資深模型師的品評</h2><p>小編邀請了資深模型師 N.Maker 熊沛文先生，他是 2023 年第 11 屆高達模型王 GBWC 大賽香港區 OVER-21 組別冠軍，亦擔任 2024 年第 12 屆高達模型王 GBWC 大賽香港區頒獎嘉賓。見到他上星期已素組了，由他品評一下這部 RG RX-78-2 元祖高達 2.0 就最好不過。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257231" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7999bbbfca1041e1bd45-479x580.jpg" alt="" width="479" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7999bbbfca1041e1bd45-479x580.jpg 479w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/7999bbbfca1041e1bd45.jpg 743w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 479px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">深模型師 N.Maker 熊沛文先生</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6fe536648e3747edb868-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6fe536648e3747edb868-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6fe536648e3747edb868.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">擔任 2024 年第 12 屆高達模型王 GBWC 大賽香港區頒獎嘉賓</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257233" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6a8d72bcc99c474bac97-433x580.jpg" alt="" width="433" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6a8d72bcc99c474bac97-433x580.jpg 433w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/6a8d72bcc99c474bac97.jpg 673w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 433px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">開箱！真香！</p><p>RG RX-78-2 元祖高達 2.0 素組完成後，外觀像是 2020 年推出的 PGU 縮小版，比起 RG 1.0 版更加強壯紮實，關節的鬆緊度非常適中，不再有以前 RG 1.0 那種鬆散的感覺，能夠輕鬆地擺動而不必擔心損壞。<a title="DSC08609" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933045988/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933045988_8a2794a6d2_h.jpg" alt="DSC08609" width="1280" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08614" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53931900537/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53931900537_f643e2dcd5_h.jpg" alt="DSC08614" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>特別值得一提的是腰部和雙腳的可動性設計非常精彩，即使在有核心戰機的情況下，腰部仍然可以大幅度彎曲，這是非常值得讚賞的設計。而雙腳在彎曲時，整個腳部的裝甲會隨之連動，這麼小的比例卻能做到這樣的結構，非常厲害。</p><p><a title="DSC08585" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933046118/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933046118_5ab6bf68f7_h.jpg" alt="DSC08585" width="1280" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08589" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933136224/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933136224_a7078f2f75_h.jpg" alt="DSC08589" width="1281" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08592" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933046113/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933046113_8dd22c9426_h.jpg" alt="DSC08592" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此外，在組裝時你會發現零件很少有傳統柱形的插槽，這使得每個零件和裝甲都可以輕鬆組裝，但又不影響鬆緊度，這大大提高了組裝的樂趣。然而，這款模型的頭部偏大，有些影響整體外觀比例。另外，廢除了可動手掌，僅提供了造型手和造型拳頭，但拳頭比例偏小，顯得不夠協調。而小腿也無法完全伸直，使得站立擺姿勢時有輕微彎曲的感覺。</p><p><a title="DSC08598" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933136144/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933136144_ea0be413c1_h.jpg" alt="DSC08598" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08599" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53932804936/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53932804936_938b93f149_h.jpg" alt="DSC08599" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC08600" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933136134/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933136134_30f310d431_h.jpg" alt="DSC08600" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>最近網上有討論頭部火炮露出的幅度不夠，與官方圖片不一致。經過觀察，確實有這個現象，火炮大約差 0.1 至 0.2 毫米才能完全露出。不過，無論從遠看還是細看，都不算大問題，大部分玩家可能根本不會注意到這點。所以，享受模型的整體設計和組裝樂趣才是最重要的，千萬別讓這些細微差距破壞了你的快樂。當然，Bandai 如何回應這個問題是另一回事。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257236" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snap0046-694x447.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snap0046-694x447.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snap0046.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這套模型在不需要複雜組裝的前提下，依然做出了出色的結構設計，是一個值得購買的產品。回想十幾年前 Bandai 推出 RG RX-78-2 時，已經覺得那款模型非常驚艷。十幾年後再做 RG 2.0，組裝過程中勾起了當年初次體驗的回憶，這真是見證時代變遷的一種感覺。</p><p><a title="DSC08603" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933136119/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933136119_fa457546bc_h.jpg" alt="DSC08603" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="DSC08608" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53932804846/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53932804846_0361d4950f_h.jpg" alt="DSC08608" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="DSC08621" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53932804766/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53932804766_9f3ed93db3_h.jpg" alt="DSC08621" width="1280" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="DSC08625" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53933252805/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53933252805_7fe0c69b9b_h.jpg" alt="DSC08625" width="1069" height="1600" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Freel%2F347474625101048%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=267&amp;t=0" width="267" height="476" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p><strong>RG 1/144 RX-78-2 高達 Ver.2.0</strong><br />
參考售價：3,850 日圓（含税）</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/rgrx782-0/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【評測】RG RX-78-2 元祖高達 2.0     資深模型師評語：感覺似 PGU 縮細版</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
