        <item>
            <title>Apple 發布無障礙主題短片《接力賽》   iPhone、Apple Watch 助殘疾運動員生活及比賽</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/apple-62/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-62</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/apple-62/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:00:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[無障礙功能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[輔助功能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257041</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>隨著奧運落幕和殘奧會臨近，Apple 近日發布一條有關無障礙主題的短片《接力賽》，講述八位殘疾和非殘疾運動員比賽的故事，當中提到的無障礙功能突顯 Apple 的多元性，為每個人的不同而設計。</p><p>繼早前的《The Greatest》及《丟失的聲音》，Apple 最近於官網及 YouTube 上載無障礙主題短片《接力賽》。片中的運動員使用 Apple 各款產品配合其日常生活、訓練及比賽，當中內置的視力、聽力、肢體活動能力、認知能力及語音等無障礙功能能配合不同用户的需要。他們亦使用各種功能來追蹤表現，如睡眠指標、每日鍛鍊目標及全天運動情況。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-2-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-2-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-4-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-4-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-4-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-5-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-5-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-5-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>影片提到 iPhone 「朗讀內容」、Apple Watch 「輔助觸控」、iPhone 「放大鏡」+「指住即讀」、Apple Watch 「輪椅體能訓練」，分別可為有視障的用户大聲朗讀文字、上肢殘障用户在不接觸螢幕的情況下使用 Apple Watch、大聲讀出視障用户指向附近實物上的文字，以及為輪椅用户提供兩種獨特的運動追蹤選項。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-694x368.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="368" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-694x368.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257044" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-1-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-1-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-3-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-3-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-3-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-8-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257051" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-8-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-8-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240819at-8-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>此外，Apple 將於今年秋季推出全新輔助功能，利用硬件和軟件為殘障用户創造全新的直觀體驗，當中包括「音樂觸覺」讓聽障礙用户在 iPhone 上體驗音樂；「語音捷徑」和「偵測非典型語音」能增強語音識別和度身訂造功能，適用於更多非典型語音用户；「眼動追蹤」讓身障用户只用眼睛就能使用 iPhone 和 iPad 等。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_52703"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BPqir3EZolw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/accessibility/the-relay/">Apple</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/apple-intelligence-7-functions/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學+實試】Apple Intelligence 7 大實用功能　一鍵校對英文文法 + TLDR 長文總結 + 錄音即時轉文字</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安裝方法 + 申請教學</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/27/apple-vision-pro-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%a1%8c%e8%b2%a8%e5%85%a8%e6%94%bb%e7%95%a5-%e5%bf%85%e8%a3%9d-app-%e3%80%81-%e6%b8%af%e7%89%88%e7%89%b9%e8%89%b2%e3%80%81%e5%a4%a7%e9%99%b8%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Vision Pro 香港行貨全攻略 :  必裝 APP 、 港版特色、大陸使用、近視及老花用家、預訂注意、開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/19/apple-62/mobile-phone/">Apple 發布無障礙主題短片《接力賽》   iPhone、Apple Watch 助殘疾運動員生活及比賽</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
